&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THIS POST IS FIXED TERM FOR 6 MONTHS DUE TO MEET THE NEEDS OF THE SERVICE &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Catering Assistant required for busy Catering operation, Ward based and central kitchen you will be required to communicate with patients taking orders for breakfast, lunch and evening meal. Replenishing water jugs serving hot and cold beverages. Regeneration at ward level catering for all dietary requirements. Cleaning duties in kitchen area.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You may be required to work in the restaurant serving customers operating a cash register may also be required to work in the main kitchen. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 8th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vivien Cartwright, Catering Support Manager&lt;br /&gt;vivien.cartwright@wales.nhs.uk&lt;br /&gt;01685 728765&lt;/p&gt;
